Interface CreatePaymentTransactionData

  • All Superinterfaces:
    PaymentInteractionData
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CreatePaymentTransactionDataImpl

    public interface CreatePaymentTransactionData
extends PaymentInteractionData
    Provides a wrapper for all data that could possibly be needed by a PaymentServiceProvider implementation to create a new payment transaction object. Created by mgatz on 7/27/16.
